item.title: Saunders Reversible Folding Umbrella
item.dc:creator: admin
item.description: Minimum order quantity is 25 units. Applicable set up charge, taxes & shipping extra. Eight panels. Auto open/close function. Fibreglass ribs. Matching coloured Plastic handle with wrist strap. Includes carry pouch. Turns inside out to prevent water dripping all over the floor. Available colours: Black, Blue Size: 21" rib length, 42" arc

item.title: Bellanca Reversible Umbrella
item.dc:creator: admin
item.description: Eight double layered panels. Fiberglass ribs. Breathable double layered inverting umbrella Straight rubberized Plastic handle. Manual open/close. Metal frame and shaft. Folds outward for storage to keep you dry and also to prevent water dripping all over the floor.
